<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Bachelor host Osher Günsberg had declared Thursday's finale would have 'an ending you won't believe'.</p>

<p>And it turns out he was very much correct - as Locky Gilbert dramatically chose Irena Srbinovska as his leading lady, leaving her love rival Bella Veralis utterly heartbroken in front of the nation. </p>

<p>In a twist no one saw coming, the 30-year-old told the two ladies he had fallen in love with them both during their final dates together - leading both to believe they had won his heart.</p>

<p>The Bachelor 2020: Irena Srbinovska WINS Locky Gilbert's heart over rival Bella Veralis in the shocking twist no one saw coming </p>

<p>A tough decision: In a twist no one saw coming, The Bachelor's Locklan 'Locky' Gilbert made the ultimate decision to start his romantic life with Irena </p>

<p>But the tense episode saw the former Survivor star break down in tears as he made the heartbreaking decision to dump Bella, and start a romantic life with her rival. </p>

<p>Prior to making his choice, the adventurous hunk revealed how difficult his choice had been.</p>

<p> 'I thought I would come here and meet one person that I like and then end up together. But I found two,' he said. </p>

<p>'They are two of the most incredible women that I've ever met in my entire life.'</p>

<p>It's all over! On Thursday night's episode, Locky finally chose between Irena Srbinovska (left) and Bella Varelis (right)</p>

<p>Irena, a 31-year-old recovery nurse, has been a fan favourite to win the show for weeks - with the handsome Bachelor regularly talking about their 'special connection' and how he loved that she 'looked after' him. </p>

<p>The sweet duo enjoyed multiple single dates together, with Irena eventually being the first to drop the 'bombshell' that she'd fallen for him.</p>

<p>But Lockie had also made it very clear he was also incredibly interested in 25-year-old Bella, stating he was charmed by her 'big brown eyes' and girl-next-door charm.</p>

<p>Fans were left aghast as he told both ladies how he was falling for them, just days before the grand finale.  </p>

<p>During the shocking episode, Locky was seen telling Irena: 'I have fallen in love with you' - before uttering the same words of adoration to Bella on their own date.</p>

<p>Before he made his choice, a giddy Irena declared: 'Knowing that he's in love with me... I feel confident knowing that this is the beginning of our future together.'</p>

<p>While Bella eagerly told producers: 'It's given me hope that everything will be alright. I mean, who tells someone they love them and then picks someone else?'</p>

<p>Playing with fire: Locky had told Bella (left) that he was beginning to fall in love with her in the drama-filled finale episode </p>
